@DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5299

### Get all departments
GET {{DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress}}/api/departments
Accept: application/json

###

### Get department by ID
GET {{DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress}}/api/departments/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new department
POST {{DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress}}/api/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Engineering",
  "description": "Software Engineering Department"
}

###

### Update department
PUT {{DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress}}/api/departments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Software Engineering",
  "description": "Updated Software Engineering Department",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Delete department
DELETE {{DepartmentAPI.API_HostAddress}}/api/departments/1

###
